<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body, table, td, p {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff !important;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }
        h2, p {
            color: #333333 !important;
        }
        /* Media query for dark mode */
        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            body {
                background-color: #121212 !important;
            }
            .container {
                background-color: #1e1e1e !important;
            }
            .logo {
                content: url('https://35fba853288929fc2c78-69cb25cc8c90ed23a3699fb2b2ac841c.ssl.cf5.rackcdn.com/email/pk-white.png') !important;
            }
            h2, p {
                color: #f4f4f4 !important;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body style="background-color: #f4f4f4 !important; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
    <tr>
        <td align="center" style="padding: 20px 0;">
            <table class="container" role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="background-color: #ffffff !important;">
                <tr>
                    <td align="left">
                        <img src="https://35fba853288929fc2c78-69cb25cc8c90ed23a3699fb2b2ac841c.ssl.cf5.rackcdn.com/email/base.png" alt="Base Hairdressing" class="logo">
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td align="left" style="padding-top: 20px;">
                        <h2 style="font-size: 24px; margin: 0; color: #333333 !important;">Thank You for Your Application to {{.SalonName}}</h2>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td align="left" style="padding-top: 10px;">
                        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #333333 !important;">
                            <strong>Hi {{.Name}},</strong>
                        </p>
                        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #333333 !important;">
                            Thank you for your interest in joining the {{.SalonName}} team!
                        </p>
                        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #333333 !important;">
                            We’re currently reviewing applications on a periodic basis due to the high volume of interest. If you don’t hear back immediately, please rest assured that your application is still under consideration.
                        </p>
                        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #333333 !important;">
                            As we have limited roles available, we carefully assess all candidates before making decisions. Once our review is complete, we’ll be in touch to update you on the next steps.
                        </p>
                        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #333333 !important;">
                            Thank you for your patience and for considering a future with us!
                        </p>
                        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; color: #333333 !important;">
                            Best regards,<br>
                            <strong>{{.SalonName}}</strong>
                        </p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>